Background

Living Sky School Division may enter into partnerships with external organizations such as First Nations Bands or other school divisions to provide services that will assist in operating safe and reliable transportation for students from external organizations, including First Nations Bands.

Procedures

Agreement
1.	Prior to providing services, Living Sky School Division and the external organization shall meet and develop an agreement which will outline the process and conditions.

2.	Fees will be set based on actual costs to the Division.

3.	The agreement may include but is not limited to:
a.	Servicing of buses.
b.	Training of drivers.
c.	Professional development of drivers and transportation staff.
d.	Transporting of students.
